Ok I'm fiannly uploading this map.
I'm getting pritty tired of argueing with people online that don't believe that I created this map.
This map was supposed to be just a muck around trainer for our RFG but I have since noticed that alot of servers are running it. The name on the wall is my email address. I didn't put my screen name on it and have since regret doing this.

But yes, I did create this map some time last year.

I'm currently working on version 4 which should be out soon if I get around to releasing it.

Anyway enjoy
